12/01/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- The defence ministry announced on Tuesday (11 January) that Albanian and US troops had completed a joint engineering exercise involving work on military and civilian projects.
Some 40 US soldiers joined Albanian troops in the exercise, which started on 15 October.
Also Tuesday, Education Minister Luan Memushi met with the leader of the Education Confederation, Xhaferr Dobrusha, to discuss employees' demands for a salary increase.
The union is threatening to stage more protests next week.
(Albanian News - 12/01/05;
AP - 11/01/05)
